《'''壮游'''》（{{lang-en|'''''The Grand Tour'''''}}）是一档由[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]制作的[[英国|英国]]<ref name="国家" /><ref name="Twitter-国家" />汽车节目，由[[杰里米·克拉克森|杰里米·克拉克森]]、[[理查德·哈蒙德|理查德·哈蒙德]]、[[詹姆斯·梅|詹姆斯·梅]]主持，并由{{link-en|安迪·威尔曼|Andy Wilman}}担任制片人。<ref name="制片人" />

在离开[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的《[[Top_Gear|Top Gear]]》后，他们四个人与[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]签约，同意在三年内制作36期系列节目。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2015/0802/718796-top-gear-trio-have-free-rein-of-am|title=Clarkson delighted with terms of new Amazon show|date=2015-08-02|accessdate=2016-12-26|quote=The new motoring show, which will be available to Amazon Prime customers next year, will feature at least 36 episodes over three years.|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224103832/http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2015/0802/718796-top-gear-trio-have-free-rein-of-am/|archivedate=2015-12-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/global/why-jeremy-clarksons-top-gear-team-went-to-amazon-1201554063|title=Why Jeremy Clarkson's 'Top Gear' Team Went to Amazon|journal=Variety|date=2015-07-31|accessdate=2016-12-26|author=Leo Barraclough|quote=will be 12 episodes in each of the three seasons, and each episode will run for around an hour. ... deal was brokered by Amazon U.K. film and TV strategy director Chris Bird and Conrad Riggs, the U.S. company's head of TV production.|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221064007/http://variety.com/2015/tv/global/why-jeremy-clarksons-top-gear-team-went-to-amazon-1201554063/|archivedate=2016-12-21}}</ref>节目每周向亚马逊Prime会员播出。2017年末，传统广播公司播出第一季的重播。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.motoringbox.com/cars/entertainment/the-grand-tour/repeats-of-the-grand-tour-are-coming-to-your-tv/|title=Repeats of The Grand Tour are coming to your TV – MotoringBox|website=www.motoringbox.com|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171001180454/http://www.motoringbox.com/cars/entertainment/the-grand-tour/repeats-of-the-grand-tour-are-coming-to-your-tv/|archivedate=2017-10-01}}</ref>{{As of|2016|12}}，节目在全世界另外195个国家和地区播出。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/b?node=12022739031|title=The Grand Tour is going global.|accessdate=2016-11-21|author=|date=|publisher=Amazon.co.uk|language=en|quote=In December, the show will premiere in 200 countries and territories around the world, exclusively on Amazon.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125042827/https://www.amazon.co.uk/b?node=12022739031|archivedate=2016-11-25}}</ref>2016年7月17日至2016年12月11日，第一季的录影棚拍摄工作在不同国家的演播帐篷内进行，第二季的演播帐篷则一直设立于[[科茨沃尔德|科茨沃尔德]]。第一季于2016年中后期拍摄，于2016年11月18日首映。第二季也于次年同一时间段拍摄，然而主持人受伤、患病导致拍摄进度延后。因此，第二季推迟至2017年12月8日上映。第三季于2018年中拍摄，2019年1月18日首播<ref>{{cite web |last=Caldecott |first=Glenn |url=https://www.radiotimes.com/news/on-demand/2018-11-27/grand-tour-s3/ |title=The Grand Tour series 3: When is it released on Amazon Prime Video? What is The Grand Tour Game? Where is it filmed? |publisher=Radio Times |date= |accessdate=2018-12-05 |archive-date=2018-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127193734/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/on-demand/2018-11-27/grand-tour-s3/ }}</ref>。

在首映日，《[[三位一体_(壮游)|三位一体]]》成为亚马逊视频的首映收视冠军。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3960150/So-DID-tune-Grand-Tour-Amazon-cagily-announces-Clarkson-s-premiere-biggest-success-Prime-Video-refuses-release-viewing-figures.html|title=So how many DID tune in to The Grand Tour? Amazon cagily announces Clarkson's premiere its 'biggest ever success' for Prime Video (but refuses to release viewing figures)|author=Martin Robinson|date=2016-11-22|accessdate=2016-12-26|work=Daily Mail|language=en|quote=Amazon Prime says its first episode has become the subscription service's biggest premiere, beating previous number one show on the service, 2015's The Man In The High Castle.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130020328/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3960150/So-DID-tune-Grand-Tour-Amazon-cagily-announces-Clarkson-s-premiere-biggest-success-Prime-Video-refuses-release-viewing-figures.html|archivedate=2016-11-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Shepherd|first=Jack|title=The Grand Tour breaks Amazon Prime streaming record with debut episode|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/the-grand-tour-amazon-prime-streaming-record-episode-1-a7431251.html|accessdate=2017-02-09|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=2016-11-22|quote=Despite the difficulty, the trio's debut was an undisputed success, becoming Amazon Prime's most-watched premiere in the streaming service's history. The previous record-holder was {{tsl|en|The Man in the High Castle (TV series)||''The Man in the High Castle''}}.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211083336/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/the-grand-tour-amazon-prime-streaming-record-episode-1-a7431251.html|archivedate=2017-02-11}}</ref>总体而言，节目得到影评人的正面评价。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-grand-tour/news/a814477/the-grand-tour-review-round-up-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-amazon-prime/ |title=The Grand Tour gets rave reviews from critics as Jeremy Clarkson and co make triumphant Amazon Prime debut |last=Warner |first=Sam |publisher=''[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]'' |publication-date=18 November 2016 |access-date=2017-01-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110165200/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-grand-tour/news/a814477/the-grand-tour-review-round-up-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-amazon-prime/ |archivedate=2017-01-10 }}</ref><ref name="dm-robinson-20161122">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3960150/So-DID-tune-Grand-Tour-Amazon-cagily-announces-Clarkson-s-premiere-biggest-success-Prime-Video-refuses-release-viewing-figures.html|title=So how many DID tune in to The Grand Tour? Amazon cagily announces Clarkson's premiere its 'biggest ever success' for Prime Video (but refuses to release viewing figures)|work=Daily Mail|date=2016-11-22|accessdate=2016-11-23|first=Martin|last=Robinson|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130020328/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3960150/So-DID-tune-Grand-Tour-Amazon-cagily-announces-Clarkson-s-premiere-biggest-success-Prime-Video-refuses-release-viewing-figures.html|archivedate=2016-11-30}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite news|title=The Grand Tour Series Premiere Review & Discussion|url=https://screenrant.com/the-grand-tour-amazon-top-gear-jeremy-clarkson/|publisher=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|accessdate=2017-11-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201041224/https://screenrant.com/the-grand-tour-amazon-top-gear-jeremy-clarkson/|archivedate=2017-12-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/nov/18/the-grand-tour-review-jeremy-clarkson-james-may-richard-hammond-leave-the-bbc-in-their-dust|title=The Grand Tour review – Clarkson and co leave the BBC in their dust|first=Sam|last=Wollaston|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2016-11-18|accessdate=2016-11-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110131933/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/nov/18/the-grand-tour-review-jeremy-clarkson-james-may-richard-hammond-leave-the-bbc-in-their-dust|archivedate=2017-01-10}}</ref>

