==== 埃博拉赛道 ====
[[File:Raf-wroughton-the-grand-tour-eboladrome-test-track-20161123.svg|thumb]]
节目拥有一条名为“埃博拉”（Eboladrome）的专用测试赛道，赛道位于[[威爾特郡|威爾特郡]]{{tsl|en|Wroughton|罗顿村}}附近的一个机场。该机场曾经用作[[英國皇家空軍|英國皇家空軍]]的{{tsl|en|RAF Wroughton|罗顿皇家空军基地}}。克拉克森表示，赛道如此命名是因为其形似[[伊波拉病毒|伊波拉病毒]]，这样设计是为了使车辆更容易犯错。赛段包括“非直道”、“在此留名”、“老妇人的房子”、“颠簸的后直道”、“变电站”和“绵羊牧场”。第一集中提到，赛道曾因为发现了一颗[[未爆炸弹药|未爆炸的二战炸弹]]而被迫修改。

第一季中，测试车辆由被称作“美国佬”的[[全國運動汽車競賽協會|纳斯卡赛事]]车手{{tsl|en|Mike Skinner|麦克·斯金纳}}驾驶。主持人表明，雇用斯金纳是节目与[[亞馬遜公司|亚马逊]]的合同义务。“美国佬”被刻画为一个拥有[[大老粗|大老粗]]口音和观点的人物，常常发表离题言论，且只以美国车为荣，对其它地区的车辆多有意见。克拉克森则在介绍中称他常把许多东西看作是[[共产主义|共产主义]]的产物。<ref name="telegraph-hogan-20161118">{{cite news| url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/the-grand-tour-vs-top-gear-how-do-they-compare/| title=''The Grand Tour'' vs ''Top Gear'': how do they compare?| work=The Daily Telegraph| first=Michael| last=Hogan| date=2016-11-18| accessdate=2016-11-26| quote=[Test driver] Mike Skinner. A stubbly, Commie-hating 59-year-old Californian prone to drawling| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127085029/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/the-grand-tour-vs-top-gear-how-do-they-compare/| archivedate=2016-11-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/allenstjohn/2016/11/17/amazons-expensive-grand-tour-is-really-just-top-gear-on-steroids/2/| title=Amazon's Expensive 'Grand Tour' Is Really Just 'Top Gear' On Steroids| date=2016-11-17| accessdate=2016-11-26| first=Allen| last=St. John| work=Forbes| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127085734/http://www.forbes.com/sites/allenstjohn/2016/11/17/amazons-expensive-grand-tour-is-really-just-top-gear-on-steroids/2/| archivedate=2016-11-27}}</ref>然而由于斯金纳评价不高，第二季中他被替换为英国赛车手{{tsl|en|Abbie Eaton|艾比·伊顿}}。<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/motors/4875936/the-grand-tour-has-scrapped-its-american-version-of-the-stig-from-season-two-of-amazon-prime-show/| title=The Grand Tour has SCRAPPED its American version of 'The Stig' from season two| date=2017-11-09| publisher=| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171112162808/https://www.thesun.co.uk/motors/4875936/the-grand-tour-has-scrapped-its-american-version-of-the-stig-from-season-two-of-amazon-prime-show/| archivedate=2017-11-12}}</ref>

在第一集播出之前，有十辆汽车预先在埃博拉赛道进行计时圈测试，并将成绩记录在圈速榜上。但节目只展示了它们的圈速，并没有展示它们的测试过程。节目展示的第一个计时圈测试是斯金纳驾驶2016年{{tsl|en|BMW 2 Series (F22)#BMW M2 (F87)|宝马M2}}，时间为1分26秒2。赛道不仅用于计时圈测试，还用于节目的常规摄影，所以除测试车辆以外，其他车辆也会出现在这条赛道，但不会被计时。
