==== 恩斯通 ====
[[Image:Enstone-airfield-the-grand-tour-gravel-test-track-20171223.svg|thumb]]
从第二季开始，节目启用位于{{tsl|en|Enstone Airfield|恩斯通机场}}的新测试赛道。恩斯通赛道地理位置靠近演播帐篷，节目组曾经计划将其用于《Top Gear》。<ref name="rufford-20171129">{{cite newspaper|url=https://www.driving.co.uk/news/interview/clarkson-hammond-and-may-on-the-grand-tour-season-2/|work=The Sunday Times: Driving|title=Our year from hell: Clarkson, Hammond and May on ''The Grand Tour'' season 2, overcoming disaster, 'that' crash and ill-health|first=Nick|last=Rufford|date=2017-11-29|accessdate=2017-12-14|quote=The show has a new test track in Enstone, ... there planning problems when [Clarkson] tried once before to use the Enstone track, back in -{Top Gear}- days ... The noisier testing of fast cars will continue to be done in Wiltshire at RAF Wroughton ... nicknamed "the Eboladrome"|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215070248/https://www.driving.co.uk/news/interview/clarkson-hammond-and-may-on-the-grand-tour-season-2/|archivedate=2017-12-15}}</ref>在新测试赛道启用后，埃博拉赛道并不会关闭，将会继续用于测试车辆。<ref name="rufford-20171129"/>

=== 明星面面碰 ===
该环节的前身是第一季的“明星脑碰脑”（Celebrity Brain Crash）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://drivetribe.com/p/the-secret-story-behind-the-grand-YpKc9wrzR6K4cetBcPJ8EA?iid=c-d5FQraQraORx4ALaUP7w |title=The Secret Story Behind The Grand Tour's Celebrity Braincrash |author=Reed, Jason |publisher=Shifting Lanes |date=2018-01-24 |accessdate=2018-01-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127004611/https://drivetribe.com/p/the-secret-story-behind-the-grand-YpKc9wrzR6K4cetBcPJ8EA?iid=c-d5FQraQraORx4ALaUP7w |archivedate=2018-01-27 }}</ref>，在这个环节中，名人嘉宾出场时总是“离奇死亡”。每当名人嘉宾“死亡”时，梅会问：“这是不是意味着他/她不会来了？”，而哈蒙德会回答道：“不会了，詹姆斯，他/她不会来了”并解释名人嘉宾的“死因”。节目的这个元素影射了[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]想要阻止《壮游》采访名人嘉宾<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2266992/jeremy-clarkson-forced-to-kill-off-charlize-theron-after-bbc-bans-star-interviews-on-the-grand-tour-over-fears-it-would-rip-off-top-gear/|title=Jeremy Clarkson forced to 'kill off' celebs on The Grand Tour after BBC 'bans Top Gear rip-off star interviews'|accessdate=2016-12-20|author=Emma Daly|date=2016-11-26|publisher=The Sun|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214130828/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2266992/jeremy-clarkson-forced-to-kill-off-charlize-theron-after-bbc-bans-star-interviews-on-the-grand-tour-over-fears-it-would-rip-off-top-gear/|archivedate=2016-12-14}}</ref>，而名人嘉宾采访曾经是《[[Top_Gear|Top Gear]]》中“[[英国疯狂汽车秀#明星开廉价车|名星开廉价车]]”环节的核心。

在收到批评之后，该环节在第二季被替换为“明星面面碰”（Celebrity Face Off）。节目每周将邀请两位拥有类似背景或关联的名人参加，两人通常来自不同国家。他们将在这个环节内驾驶汽车进行计时圈比赛。此环节使用的车辆为[[捷豹F-Type|捷豹F-Type R-Dynamic]]，使用的赛道为位于恩斯通的半碎石、半铺装赛道。克拉克森会采访两位嘉宾，随后公布两者的圈速。

