== 节目制作 ==
节目环节的设计需要保证与团队在[[BBC|BBC]]制作的《[[Top_Gear|Top Gear]]》有所区别。<ref name="与Top Gear的区别1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2266992/jeremy-clarkson-forced-to-kill-off-charlize-theron-after-bbc-bans-star-interviews-on-the-grand-tour-over-fears-it-would-rip-off-top-gear/|title=Jeremy Clarkson forced to 'kill off' celebs on The Grand Tour after BBC 'bans Top Gear rip-off star interviews'|accessdate=2016-12-14|author=Emma Daly|date=2016-11-26|publisher=The Sun|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214130828/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2266992/jeremy-clarkson-forced-to-kill-off-charlize-theron-after-bbc-bans-star-interviews-on-the-grand-tour-over-fears-it-would-rip-off-top-gear/|archivedate=2016-12-14}}</ref><ref name="与Top Gear的区别2">{{Cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/the-grand-tour-vs-top-gear-how-do-they-compare/|title=The Grand Tour vs Top Gear: how do they compare?|accessdate=2016-12-14|author=Michael Hogan|date=2017-01-24|work=The Telegragh|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127085029/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/the-grand-tour-vs-top-gear-how-do-they-compare/|archivedate=2016-11-27}}</ref>在周游世界的[[壮游|壮游]]之中，节目会在巨大的帐篷里进行拍摄。主持人环绕一张支架活动桌而坐，观众则坐在他们面前。唠嗑街环节讨论节目拍摄时的[[新闻|新闻时事]]。[[#测试赛道|车辆圈速]]则展示于一旁的电子计分板上。[[全國運動汽車競賽協會|纳斯卡赛事]]车手{{tsl|en|Mike Skinner||麦克·斯金纳}}充当节目的试车手，有着[[大老粗|大老粗]]的美国南方口音和观点，发表不着边际的言论。<ref name="与Top Gear的区别2" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/allenstjohn/2016/11/17/amazons-expensive-grand-tour-is-really-just-top-gear-on-steroids|title=Amazon's Expensive 'Grand Tour' Is Really Just 'Top Gear' On Steroids|accessdate=2016-12-14|author=Allen St. John|date=2016-11-17|publisher=Forbes|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222165246/http://www.forbes.com/sites/allenstjohn/2016/11/17/amazons-expensive-grand-tour-is-really-just-top-gear-on-steroids/|archivedate=2016-12-22}}</ref>明星脑碰脑环节的所有名人嘉宾都会在主持人介绍之后“离奇死亡”。