克拉克森、哈蒙德和梅皆曾经担任[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]汽车节目《Top Gear》的主持人。旧版节目中三人轮流担任主持人，2002年节目重启后担任永久主持人，直至2015年。在他们担任主持人期间，节目在全球拥有大约3.5亿观众，并被[[吉尼斯世界纪录大全|吉尼斯世界纪录大全]]认证为最多人观看的纪实类电视节目。<ref name="bbc topgear">{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/business-31832534 | title = Top Gear: How a monster was born | date = 2015-03-11 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[BBC|BBC]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180113062249/http://www.bbc.com/news/business-31832534 | archivedate = 2018-01-13 }}</ref>由于多件涉及的克拉克森事件发生，2015年3月，[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]决定不再与克拉克森续约。另一方面，公司向梅和哈蒙德提供丰厚的薪水请他们再制作新的一季节目，但他们表示如果没有克拉克森，他们也不会留在《Top Gear》。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/top-gear-bbc-has-offered-richard-hammond-and-james-may-1-million-to-return-10296336.html | title = Top Gear: 'BBC has offered Richard Hammond and James May £4.6 million to return' | first = Matilda | last = Battersby | date = 2015-06-05 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Independent|The Independent]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104132455/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/top-gear-bbc-has-offered-richard-hammond-and-james-may-1-million-to-return-10296336.html | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref>一同离开的还有《Top Gear》的制作人，克拉克森的同学安迪·威尔曼。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-32437814 | title = Top Gear producer Andy Wilman quits show | date = 2015-04-24 | accessdate = 2017-01-03 | work = [[BBC|BBC]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160724101637/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-32437814 | archivedate = 2016-07-24 }}</ref>2016年，英国广播公司为节目请来新主持人{{tsl|en|Chris Evans (presenter)|克里斯·埃文斯}}和[[马特·勒布朗|马特·勒布朗]]。

克拉克森离开英国广播公司后不久便表示希望打造一档新的汽车节目，并说“我失去了我的孩子，但我应该再创造另一个。我不知道孩子的母亲是谁，也不知道孩子会是什么样”。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/apr/18/jeremy-clarkson-top-gear-car-show-bbc | title = Jeremy Clarkson says he had cancer scare two days before Top Gear fracas | first = Hannah | last = Ellis-Petersen | date = 2015-04-28 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104073146/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/apr/18/jeremy-clarkson-top-gear-car-show-bbc | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref>2015年4月开始，传闻称，克拉克森、哈蒙德和梅正低调地接触多家广播公司。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/top-gear-trio-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-and-james-may-meet-for-secret-talks-at-goodwood-motor-10216651.html | title = Top Gear trio Jeremy Clarkson, Richard Hammond and James May meet for 'secret talks' at Goodwood Motor Circuit | first = Daisy | last = Wyatt | date = 2015-04-30 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Independent|The Independent]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104073113/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/top-gear-trio-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-and-james-may-meet-for-secret-talks-at-goodwood-motor-10216651.html | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/may/08/top-gear-jeremy-clarkson-james-may-richard-hammond-itv-bbc | title = Top Gear stars Jeremy Clarkson, James May and Richard Hammond in ITV talks | first1 = John | last1 = Plunkett | first2 = Mark | last2 = Sweney | date = 2015-05-08 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104073047/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/may/08/top-gear-jeremy-clarkson-james-may-richard-hammond-itv-bbc | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref>这些传闻指出，三人可能会选择一家美国的广播公司，因为克拉克森的[[竞业条款|竞业条款]]不允许他为[[独立电视台_(频道)|独立电视台]]等英国广播公司的竞争对手制作汽车节目。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/jeremy-clarksons-lawyers-confident-he-can-get-around-bbc-ban-on-making-top-gear-style-programme-for-10383299.html | title = Jeremy Clarkson's lawyers confident he can get around BBC contract ban on doing Top Gear-style show for ITV | first = Matilda | last = Battersby | date = 2015-07-12 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Independent|The Independent]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104073357/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/jeremy-clarksons-lawyers-confident-he-can-get-around-bbc-ban-on-making-top-gear-style-programme-for-10383299.html | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref>在他们接触的广播公司中，[[Netflix|Netflix]]认为克拉克森的团队要求的经费过多，[[英国电信体育台|英国电信体育台]]则认为这档节目更适合一个拥有全球业务的广播公司。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-34167864 | title = Netflix: Top Gear trio 'not worth the money' | date = 2015-09-06 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[BBC|BBC]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180113060730/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-34167864 | archivedate = 2018-01-13 }}</ref>

2015年7月，克拉克森宣布，他与[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊公司]]签订合同，制作一档与《Top Gear》类似的全新汽车节目。哈蒙德和梅将共同主持，威尔曼担任制作人。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.standard.co.uk/news/celebritynews/amazon-sign-top-gears-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-and-james-may-for-new-show-10426102.html | title = Amazon Prime sign Top Gear's Jeremy Clarkson, Richard Hammond and James May for exclusive new show | first = Jonathan | last = Pyrnn | date = 2015-07-30 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = {{tsl|en|London Evening Standard|London Evening Standard|The Evening Standard}} | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104132414/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/celebritynews/amazon-sign-top-gears-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-and-james-may-for-new-show-10426102.html | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref>合同要求制作三季共36期节目，从2016年起向[[Amazon_Prime|Amazon Prime]]会员放映。威尔曼表示，亚马逊将保证他们制作节目的自由，并提供足够的资金。同时，由于节目采用服务订阅模式而非广告投放模式，他们不必承受来自赞助商的商业压力。<ref name="variety why">{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2015/tv/global/why-jeremy-clarksons-top-gear-team-went-to-amazon-1201554063/ | title = Why Jeremy Clarkson's 'Top Gear' Team Went to Amazon | first = Leo | last = Barraclough | date = 2015-07-31 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170110020423/https://variety.com/2015/tv/global/why-jeremy-clarksons-top-gear-team-went-to-amazon-1201554063/ | archivedate = 2017-01-10 }}</ref>亚马逊CEO[[杰夫·贝索斯|杰夫·贝索斯]]称能把这档节目带来亚马逊令他“非常兴奋”，节目的制作将会“非常、非常、非常昂贵”。他还补充道，“（克拉克森、哈蒙德和梅）值得花费这么多钱，而且他们自己也清楚这一点”。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/amazon/11800890/jeff-bezos-interview-amazon-prime-jeremy-clarkson.html | title = Amazon's Jeff Bezos: With Jeremy Clarkson, we're entering a new golden age of television | first = James | last = Quinn | date = 2015-08-15 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171213161153/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/amazon/11800890/jeff-bezos-interview-amazon-prime-jeremy-clarkson.html | archivedate = 2017-12-13 }}</ref>根据《[[每日镜报|每日镜报]]》报道，亚马逊共为这三季节目支付1.6亿英镑。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/11829887/Jeremy-Clarkson-set-to-become-highest-paid-TV-host-in-Britain-on-post-Top-Gear-Amazon-Prime-show.html | title = Jeremy Clarkson 'to become highest paid TV host in Britain' on post-Top Gear Amazon Prime show | first = Lucy | last = Clarke-Billings | date = 2015-08-28 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180123003925/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/11829887/Jeremy-Clarkson-set-to-become-highest-paid-TV-host-in-Britain-on-post-Top-Gear-Amazon-Prime-show.html | archivedate = 2018-01-23 }}</ref>威尔曼否认节目花费了这么多钱，但承认节目确实很昂贵，部分原因是亚马逊坚持以[[4K分辨率|4K分辨率]]拍摄。<ref name="variety wilman">{{Cite web | url = https://variety.com/2016/tv/global/the-grand-tour-executive-producer-andy-wilman-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-1201844223/ | title = 'The Grand Tour' Executive Producer Andy Wilman on Working With Jeremy Clarkson, Richard Hammond, James May | first = Leo | last = Barraclough | date = 2016-08-25 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104132352/http://variety.com/2016/tv/global/the-grand-tour-executive-producer-andy-wilman-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-1201844223/ | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref>节目主要在英国进行制作，由克拉克森、哈蒙德、梅和威尔曼创立的制作公司W Chump & Sons负责制作工作。<ref name="variety why"/>

2016年5月，节目组公布节目的名称为“The Grand Tour”。克拉克森表示，这个名称来源于[[壮游|壮游]]的传统，反映节目将在多个不同国家进行拍摄。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-36267294 | title = The Grand Tour: Amazon reveal Clarkson, May and Hammond show name | date = 2016-05-11 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[BBC|BBC]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180113062236/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-36267294 | archivedate = 2018-01-13 }}</ref>在正式公布节目名称之前，一间与节目相关的公司申请了一个名为“Gear Knobs”的商标<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/motoring/top-gear/11871854/Jeremy-Clarksons-new-Amazon-Top-Gear-style-show-could-be-called-Gear-Knobs.html|title=Jeremy Clarkson's new Amazon Top Gear-style show could be called Gear Knobs|accessdate=2017-01-24|author=Helena Horton|date=2015-09-17|work=Daily Telegraph|language=en|quote='Gear Knobs' is trademarked to new company Newincco 1361 Limited which has also trademarked 'Gear Nobs', and the name 'Speedbird' which is speculated to be a charater [''[[sic|sic]]''] on the show.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202201125/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/motoring/top-gear/11871854/Jeremy-Clarksons-new-Amazon-Top-Gear-style-show-could-be-called-Gear-Knobs.html|archivedate=2016-12-02}}</ref>，但在2015年10月，克拉克森表明这不是节目的名称。<ref>{{Cite tweet|author=Jeremy Clarkson|user=JeremyClarkson|number=652539027476889600|date=2015-10-09|accessdate=2017-01-24|title=I see that many people think our new show is called Gear Knobs. Well you heard it here first. It isn't.|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://jalopnik.com/the-top-gear-guys-new-amazon-show-will-not-be-called-ge-1735830025|title=The Top Gear Guys' New Amazon Show Will Not Be Called 'Gear Knobs,' Thankfully|accessdate=2016-01-01|author=Alanis King|date=2015-10-09|publisher=Jalopnik|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101013502/http://jalopnik.com/the-top-gear-guys-new-amazon-show-will-not-be-called-ge-1735830025|archivedate=2016-01-01}}</ref>2016年4月，克拉克森解释道，由于法律原因，“Gear”这个单词不能被用于新节目的名称。<ref>{{Cite tweet|author=Jeremy Clarkson|user=JeremyClarkson|number=718433796962533377|date=2016-04-08|accessdate=2017-01-24|title=Thanks for your suggestions. But be aware: for legal reasons, we cannot use a name with the word "gear" in it.|language=en}}</ref>

