最初，节目的形式为每一集展示单独的[[电视电影|电视电影]]，皆为[[外景拍摄|外景拍摄]]而没有录影棚环节。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/mar/25/james-may-top-gear-cenotaph-stunt-amazon-prime-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond|title=James May: Top Gear's Cenotaph stunt was 'possibly a little unwise'|work=Guardian|first=John|last=Plunkett|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-04-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404175423/http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/mar/25/james-may-top-gear-cenotaph-stunt-amazon-prime-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond|archivedate=2016-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2016/mar/27/james-may-chris-evans-top-gear-amazon|title=James May: 'We are not in a race with Chris Evans' Top Gear'|work=Guardian|first=John|last=Plunkett|date=2016-03-27|accessdate=2016-04-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405093856/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2016/mar/27/james-may-chris-evans-top-gear-amazon|archivedate=2016-04-05}}</ref>随后，节目决定跟随“The Grand Tour”这一名称的含义，使用帐篷充当移动录影棚。这样他们不仅能邀请当地的观众，还能让主持人驾车探索当地文化。<ref name="variety wilman"/>威尔曼表示，克拉克森在观看了一集[[浸礼宗|浸礼宗]]典礼中的《[[真探|真探]]》后萌生了在帐篷中拍摄观众环节的想法。<ref name="variety wilman"/>

2018年12月13日，据宣布第四季节目形式有所变化<ref>{{cite news|url=https://twitter.com/thegrandtour/status/1073326356321222656|title=The Grand Tour: Series 4|work=Twitter|date=2018-12-13|accessdate=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108105513/https://twitter.com/thegrandtour/status/1073326356321222656}}</ref>。帐蓬录影棚不再使用，着力于大制作的车辆特辑。三位主持人也会根据各自的喜欢，录制个人节目<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/reality-tv/a25578807/the-grand-tour-renewed-series-4-major-format-changes/|title=The Grand Tour Renewed Series 4 Major Format Changes|work=DigitalSpy|first=Justin|last=Harp|date=2018-12-14|accessdate=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216190122/https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/reality-tv/a25578807/the-grand-tour-renewed-series-4-major-format-changes/}}</ref>。

=== 法律问题 ===

威尔曼表示，亚马逊的律师非常留意环节中任何与《Top Gear》之间的相似点，并要求对环节样式进行修改。<ref name="sun-daly-20161126"/><ref name="telegraph-hogan-20161118"/>明星开廉价车、酷车墙、试替哥等来自《Top Gear》的元素都不能再使用，同时他们还要明确其他法律问题。例如，律师表示，他们可以在测试赛道中测试汽车，但不能像《Top Gear》般手写出车辆的圈速并展示于圈速榜上，只能转为使用电子圈速榜。<ref name="telegraph legal">{{cite web | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/08/24/jeremy-clarksons-new-show-cannot-have-a-test-track-or-describe-n/ | title = Jeremy Clarkson's new show cannot have a test track or describe Namibia as 'beautiful' over fears of being sued, producer claims | first = Patrick | last = Foster | date = 2016-08-24 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = [[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180104080252/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/08/24/jeremy-clarksons-new-show-cannot-have-a-test-track-or-describe-n/ | archivedate = 2018-01-04 }}</ref>威尔曼还称，有些律师的顾虑“变得越来越古怪”，例如梅是否能说“cock”，或者在旅途中主持人是否能停下欣赏风景并称赞“这真美”。<ref name="telegraph legal"/>

一些报道称，英国广播公司明确地向剧组表示他们不能邀请名人嘉宾或让名人嘉宾在赛道上比赛。<ref name="sun-daly-20161126">{{cite news|url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2266992/jeremy-clarkson-forced-to-kill-off-charlize-theron-after-bbc-bans-star-interviews-on-the-grand-tour-over-fears-it-would-rip-off-top-gear/|title=Jeremy Clarkson forced to 'kill off' celebs on The Grand Tour after BBC 'bans Top Gear rip-off star interviews'|work=[[太阳报_(英国)|The Sun]]|date=2016-11-26|accessdate=2016-11-26|first=Emma|last=Daly|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161214130828/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2266992/jeremy-clarkson-forced-to-kill-off-charlize-theron-after-bbc-bans-star-interviews-on-the-grand-tour-over-fears-it-would-rip-off-top-gear/|archivedate=2016-12-14}}</ref>随后这被证实是假消息，节目组称，环节没有邀请名人嘉宾的真实原因是团队临阵脱逃了。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://drivetribe.com/p/the-secret-story-behind-the-grand-YpKc9wrzR6K4cetBcPJ8EA?iid=WUX2vundQZGKNt5segP2wQ|title=The Secret Story Behind The Grand Tour's Celebrity Braincrash|last=Reed, Jason|first=|date=2018-01-23|website=DriveTribe|publisher=Shifting Lanes|access-date=2018-01-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127004615/https://drivetribe.com/p/the-secret-story-behind-the-grand-YpKc9wrzR6K4cetBcPJ8EA?iid=WUX2vundQZGKNt5segP2wQ|archivedate=2018-01-27}}</ref>

“明星脑碰脑”环节在第二季中被替换为“明星面面碰”，两名嘉宾在这个环节中进行计时圈比赛，以此回避与英国广播公司间的法律问题。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vulture.com/2017/12/the-grand-tour-season-2-top-gear-changes.html | title = 3 Big Ways The Grand Tour Went Back to Its Top Gear Roots for Season Two | first = Devon | last = Ivie | date = 2017-12-11 | accessdate = 2018-01-03 | work = {{tsl|en|Vulture (magazine)|Vulture}} | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171211210549/http://www.vulture.com/2017/12/the-grand-tour-season-2-top-gear-changes.html | archivedate = 2017-12-11 }}</ref>

=== 拍摄 ===
荷兰的联合广播机构（United Broadcast Facilities）赢得了帐篷环节实况转播的合约。<ref name="录影技术" />十四个麦克风用于录制帐篷中观众的[[罐头笑声|背景笑声]]。<ref name="录影技术" />移动录影棚的声音设置使用了{{link-en|Lawo|Lawo}}调音台，连接了{{link-en|MADI|MADI}}用于{{link-en|实时混音|Live sound mixing}}、录音和{{link-en|对讲系统|Talkback (recording)}}的通信。<ref name="录影技术" />

第一季中，录影棚环节在世界各地的不同地点进行拍摄。2016年7月17日，录影棚部分在[[南非|南非]][[约翰内斯堡|约翰内斯堡]]开始拍摄。<ref name="Twitter-2016-07-17">{{Cite tweet|author=Jeremy Clarkson|user=JeremyClarkson|number=754582342228971520|date=2016-07-17|accessdate=2017-01-24|title=This is it. The Grand Tour's first studio day.|language=en}}</ref>[[美国|美国]][[南加利福尼亞州|南加利福利亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的拍摄于2016年9月25日进行，而[[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]的拍摄则于2016年11月21日进行。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.roadandtrack.com/car-culture/entertainment/news/a31281/the-grand-tour-nashville/|title=The Grand Tour Will Tape In Nashville, Here's How to Get Tickets|accessdate=2016-11-21|author=Chris Perkins|date=2016-10-24|publisher=Road & Track|language=en|quote=Amazon announced Monday that The Grand Tour will tape an episode in Nashville, Tenn. on November 21st.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161123205933/http://www.roadandtrack.com/car-culture/entertainment/news/a31281/the-grand-tour-nashville/|archivedate=2016-11-23}}</ref>[[英国|英国]]的录影棚部分于2016年11月13日在[[北约克郡|北约克郡]][[惠特比|惠特比]]进行拍摄，<ref name="Twitter-2017-01-24">{{Cite tweet|author=Jeremy Clarkson|user=JeremyClarkson|number=781527444713041920|date=2016-09-29|accessdate=2017-01-24|title=Grand Tour show one: Los Angeles. Show two: Johannesburg. Show three: Whitby obviously. Tickets available now.|language=en}}</ref>并于2016年12月在[[尼斯湖|尼斯湖]]进行进一步拍摄。[[荷兰|荷兰]][[鹿特丹|鹿特丹]]的拍摄在2016年10月22日进行，[[芬兰|芬兰]][[拉普蘭區|拉普兰区]]的拍摄则在2016年11月3日进行。<ref name="Twitter-2016-10-22">{{Cite tweet|author=The Grand Tour|user=thegrandtour|number=789851989958164480|date=2016-10-22|accessdate=2017-01-24|title=Thank you for a great show Rotterdam.|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite tweet|author=Jeremy Clarkson|user=JeremyClarkson|number=794221040448733184|date=2016-11-03|accessdate=2017-01-24|title=Very enjoyable Grand Tour recording in Finland today. Epic audience|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Facebook-2016-10-11">{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/thegrandtour/posts/510854715779741|title=The Grand Tour – Timeline|accessdate=2017-01-24|author=The Grand Tour|date=2016-10-11|publisher=Facebook|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617120352/https://www.facebook.com/thegrandtour/posts/510854715779741|archivedate=2018-06-17}}</ref>[[德国|德国]][[斯图加特|斯图加特]]（[[路德维希堡|路德维希堡]]）也进行了拍摄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/gp/video/splash/TGTWaitlist|title=Amazon Instant Video|accessdate=2016-10-25|author=|date=|publisher=Amazon.de|language=de|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019211934/https://www.amazon.de/gp/video/splash/TGTWaitlist|archivedate=2016-10-19}}</ref>最后一场录影棚摄影在2016年12月于[[杜拜|迪拜]]进行。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-grand-tour/news/a813329/the-grand-tour-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-dubai/|title=The final location for Jeremy Clarkson's The Grand Tour has been unveiled|accessdate=2016-11-21|author=Lucy Morris|date=2016-11-07|publisher=Digital Spy|language=en|quote=their final stop will be at the base of the world's tallest tower - the Burj Khalifa - in the beating heart of downtown Dubai.|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122013015/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-grand-tour/news/a813329/the-grand-tour-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-dubai/|archivedate=2016-11-22}}</ref>

第二季中，克拉克森染上肺炎，哈蒙德发生车祸，制作人决定这一季不会有移动的演播帐篷。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2017/aug/13/jeremy-clarkson-pneumonia-mallorca|title=Jeremy Clarkson reveals he nearly died from pneumonia in hospital|publisher=theguardian.com|date=2017-08-13|accessdate=2017-12-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203170517/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2017/aug/13/jeremy-clarkson-pneumonia-mallorca|archivedate=2017-12-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2017/jun/10/richard-hammond-car-crash-switzerland-the-grand-tour-top-gear|title=Richard Hammond airlifted to hospital following car crash in Switzerland|publisher=theguardian.com|date=2017-06-11|accessdate=2017-12-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206135811/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2017/jun/10/richard-hammond-car-crash-switzerland-the-grand-tour-top-gear|archivedate=2017-12-06}}</ref>帐篷将被固定于克拉克森在[[科茨沃尔德|科茨沃尔德]]的家附近，方便团队进行操作，同时也给明星面面碰等新环节提供便利。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.businessinsider.com/the-grand-tour-jeremy-clarksons-show-moves-to-new-cotswolds-base-2017-9|title=Jeremy Clarkson's found a new permanent home for his Amazon show|publisher=uk.businessinsider.com|date=2017-09-26|accessdate=2017-12-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211011559/http://uk.businessinsider.com/the-grand-tour-jeremy-clarksons-show-moves-to-new-cotswolds-base-2017-9|archivedate=2017-12-11}}</ref>2017年9月，[[西牛津郡|西牛津郡]]地方议会准许节目组在[[奇平诺顿|奇平诺顿]]附近的{{tsl|en|Great Tew|大图村}}（Great Tew Estate）设置帐篷进行三个月的拍摄。<ref name="grubb-20170909">{{cite newspaper|url=http://www.oxfordmail.co.uk/news/15524882.Plans_passed_for_TV_filming_rumoured_to_be_Jeremy_Clarkson_s_The_Grand_Tour/|title=Plans passed for TV filming rumoured to be Jeremy Clarkson's The Grand Tour|date=2017-09-09|accessdate=2017-12-14|first=Sophie|last=Grubb|work={{tsl|en|Oxford Mail|Oxford Mail}}|quote=[[西牛津郡|West Oxfordshire District Council]] has given approval for 13 weeks of filming at the {{tsl|en|Great Tew|Great Tew}} Estate, near Chipping Norton. ... temporary studio ... {{tsl|en|W. Chump & Sons|Chump Productions}}, the production company owned by Jeremy Clarkson, James May, Richard Hammond and producer Andy Wilman. ... shoot will involve 80 staff members and 350 ticketed guests, with the latter expected to generate 150–200 cars on a filming day. ... during two five-week periods between October and December. ... 200 parking spaces, a marquee and a catering bus ... parking during the Cornbury festival will be utilised|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215000637/http://www.oxfordmail.co.uk/news/15524882.Plans_passed_for_TV_filming_rumoured_to_be_Jeremy_Clarkson_s_The_Grand_Tour/|archivedate=2017-12-15}}</ref>此前为{{tsl|en|Cornbury Music Festival|康伯里音乐节}}准备的200个停车位可以满足80名工作人员以及每周350名游客的需要。<ref name="grubb-20170909"/>第二季拍摄工作的时间窗口为2017年10月－12月。<ref name="grubb-20170909"/>

=== 技术问题 ===
第二季的拍摄过程中，制作团队遇到了帐篷内的灯光问题，导致摄影工作脱轨。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://drivetribe.com/p/heres-what-a-real-day-of-filming-a8aT5x3TRHy1Ls5Qawutqw?iid=H7nwzGfUTiuWgH0HTpnt8A|title=Here's What A Real Day of Filming The Grand Tour Is Like|author=Reed, Jason|first=|date=2018-01-25|website={{tsl|en|DriveTribe||DriveTribe}}|publisher=Shifting Lanes|accessdate=2018-01-26|platform=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127004613/https://drivetribe.com/p/heres-what-a-real-day-of-filming-a8aT5x3TRHy1Ls5Qawutqw?iid=H7nwzGfUTiuWgH0HTpnt8A|archivedate=2018-01-27}}</ref>尽管如此，所有剧集都在原定的日期上映，避免了推迟。

