ine.co.uk/article/jeremy-clarkson-grand-tour-box-video|archivedate=2016-12-28}}</ref>节目第一集表明，赞助商包括{{link-en|百年灵喷气机队|Breitling Jet Team}}、[[DHL|DHL]]和[[三星集团|三星集团]]。<ref>{{cite episode|title=The Holy Trinity|date=2016-11-17|accessdate=2017-01-24|series=The Grand Tour|network=Amazon Video|series-no=1|number=1|time=01:10:45|language=en|quote=Promotional Consideration {{unbulleted list|{{link-en|Breitling Jet Team|Breitling Jet Team}}|[[DHL|DHL]]|[[三星集团|Samsung]]}}}}</ref>八架百年灵喷气式飞机参加了开幕飞行表演。<ref>{{cite tweet|user=thegrandtour|author=The Grand Tour|number=799946703390593024|date=2016-11-19|accessdate=2017-01-24|title=8 Breitling jets, the #BurningVan festival, and a flotilla of over 40 cars. Stream episode 1 of #TheGrandTour on Amazon Prime Video now.|language=en}}</ref>第二集中，{{link-en|5.11 Tactical|5.11 Tactical}}也成为了赞助商之一。第五集的片头中出现了一架DHL的[[波音757|波音757]]飞机，同时，DHL的商标也出现在埃博拉赛道的防撞栏上。这一集的演播帐篷位于荷兰[[鹿特丹|鹿特丹]]。

== 评价 ==
{{As of|2016|11}}，节目受到评论员积极的评价。<ref name="#1"/>《[[每日快报|每日快报]]》记者尼拉·德纳斯（Neela Debnath）认为，节目第一季“就像是一部好莱坞大片”，“（《壮游》令人感觉是）服用了类固醇的《Top Gear》”。<ref name="dm-robinson-20161122">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3960150/So-DID-tune-Grand-Tour-Amazon-cagily-announces-Clarkson-s-premiere-biggest-success-Prime-Video-refuses-release-viewing-figures.html|title=So how many DID tune in to The Grand Tour? Amazon cagily announces Clarkson's premiere its 'biggest ever success' for Prime Video (but refuses to release viewing figures)|work=Daily Mail|date=2016-11-22|accessdate=2016-11-23|first=Martin|last=Robinson|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130020328/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3960150/So-DID-tune-Grand-Tour-Amazon-cagily-announces-Clarkson-s-premiere-biggest-success-Prime-Video-refuses-release-viewing-figures.html|archivedate=2016-11-30}}</ref>然而[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]美术编辑{{tsl|en|Will Gompertz|威尔·冈珀茨}}（Will Gompertz）却表示节目片头“毫无反讽，感觉傲慢，令人不适”，但当主持人回到演播帐篷后，“节目原来的感觉回来了。对于我来说，《壮游》这档电视节目想要成为、也应该成为一部电影”。<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-38024595 |title=The Grand Tour Review: Clarkson returns in 'filmic' show |last=Gompertz |first=Will |date=2016-11-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129035139/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-38024595 |archivedate=2016-11-29 }}</ref>《[[独立报|独立报]]》将《壮游》描述成“拥有更多预算的、最好的《最高档》”。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/the-grand-tour-episode-1-review-top-gear-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-amazon-prime-a7424556.html|title=The Grand Tour episode 1 review: The best of Top Gear with a bigger budget|date=2016-11-18|newspaper=The Independent|language=en-GB|access-date=2016-11-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127024004/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/the-grand-tour-episode-1-review-top-gear-jeremy-clarkson-richard-hammond-james-may-amazon-prime-a7424556.html|archivedate=2016-11-27}}</ref>《TheWrap》报道称，交响乐先进媒体（Symphony Advanced Media）预计，节目上映首周吸引的观众是《[[高堡奇人_(电视剧)|高堡奇人]]》的三倍。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thewrap.com/the-grand-tour-tv-ratings-man-in-high-castle-amazon/|title=Amazon's 'Grand Tour' Triples 'Man in the High Castle' Viewers|format=Exclusive|first=Tony|last=Maglio|date=2016-11-28|accessdate=2016-11-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118205110/http://www.thewrap.com/the-grand-tour-tv-ratings-man-in-high-castle-amazon/|archivedate=2017-01-18}}</ref>

节目第二集收到评论员的正面评价相对较少。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》评论此集中约旦的桥段时表示，“……这个单调乏味的动作电影桥段表明他们有些迷失了自我，亚马逊给予节目组制作的自由，但这可能有负面影响。”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/2016/11/25/grand-tour-episode-twooperation-desert-stumble-clarkson-still/|title=The Grand Tour episode two review: Operation Desert Stumble and Jeremy Clarkson is still off the leash – plus all the talking points|work=The Telegraph|date=2016-11-25|accessdate=2016-11-25|first=Ed|last=Power|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125015522/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/2016/11/25/grand-tour-episode-twooperation-desert-stumble-clarkson-still/|archivedate=2016-11-25}}</ref>《[[广播时报|广播时报]]》称，“许多观众对这一集感到不满，认为这档节目很乏味”。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-11-25/viewers-divided-over-difficult-second-episode-of-the-grand-tour|title=Viewers divided over "difficult second episode" of The Grand Tour|newspaper=RadioTimes|access-date=2016-11-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126145424/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-11-25/viewers-divided-over-difficult-second-episode-of-the-grand-tour|archivedate=2016-11-26}}</ref>

[[理查德·哈蒙德|理查德·哈蒙德]]在第六集中暗示吃冰淇淋的男性为同性恋，因此遭到{{tsl|en|Stonewall (charity)|石墙慈善机构}}、{{tsl|en|Peter Tatchell|彼得·塔切尔}}（Peter Tatchell）、[[奥利·亚历山大|奥利·亚历山大]]（Olly Alexander）的批评。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/dec/27/richard-hammond-ice-cream-gay-the-grand-tour|title=Richard Hammond under fire for 'ice-cream is gay' line on The Grand Tour|first=Elle|last=Hunt|date=2016-12-27|accessdate=2016-12-31|quote=In front of a live audience, Clarkson pointed to an image of the interior of a Rolls Royce, saying: "The only problem is that in one of those, you couldn't enjoy a chocolate Magnum ice-cream." "It's all right, I don't eat ice-cream", replied Hammond. "It's something to do with being straight."|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230165725/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2016/dec/27/richard-hammond-ice-cream-gay-the-grand-tour|archivedate=2016-12-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/38442533/richard-hammond-is-criticised-for-gay-ice-cream-joke-on-amazon-show-the-grand-tour|title=Richard Hammond is criticised for gay ice cream joke on Amazon show, The Grand Tour|date=2016-12-27|accessdate=2016-12-31|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230102209/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/38442533/richard-hammond-is-criticised-for-gay-ice-cream-joke-on-amazon-show-the-grand-tour|archivedate=2016-12-30}}</ref>随后的报道称，哈蒙德的这个暗示是在讽刺芬兰一个有争议的电视广告。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Boyle|first1=Simon|title=Richard Hammond's controversial 'gay ice cream joke' on The Grand Tour may not have been all it seemed|url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2518591/richard-hammonds-controversial-gay-ice-cream-joke-on-the-grand-tour-may-not-have-been-all-it-seemed/|accessdate=2017-02-03|work=The Sun|date=2017-01-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170203163841/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/2518591/richard-hammonds-controversial-gay-ice-cream-joke-on-the-grand-tour-may-not-have-been-all-it-seemed/|archivedate=2017-02-03}}</ref>

在2017年{{tsl|en|Television and Radio Industries Club|电视和广播行业俱乐部}}奖中，《壮游》获得了一个原创OTT流媒体类别的奖项提名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tric.org.uk/2017awardsnominees.php|title=2017 TRIC Award Nominees|publisher={{tsl|en|Television and Radio Industries Club|Television and Radio Industries Club}}|accessdate=2017-02-28|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301180426/http://www.tric.org.uk/2017awardsnominees.php}}</ref>

来自《[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]》的凯文·约曼（Kevin Yeoman）给予节目积极的评价。他表示，“粉丝们能放心，《Top Gear》没有走远，它只是换了个名字藏在了亚马逊”。<ref name="#2"/>《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的索尼娅·沙莱雅（Sonia Saraiya）也同样对节目给予好评，她表示，“当提到汽车，《壮游》肯定能满足车迷……克拉克森、哈蒙德和梅对机械的喜爱……还在，仍然纯粹且引人入胜，哪怕节目已经转变为一档网络节目。”<ref>{{cite news|title=TV Review: Jeremy Clarkson’s ‘The Grand Tour’ on Amazon|url=https://variety.com/2016/tv/reviews/tv-review-grand-tour-amazon-jeremy-clarkson-top-gear-1201922066/|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2017-11-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201043903/http://variety.com/2016/tv/reviews/tv-review-grand-tour-amazon-jeremy-clarkson-top-gear-1201922066/|archivedate=2017-12-01}}</ref>

然而与之相反，2017年4月，《CarScoops》的布莱德·安德森（Brad Anderson）表示，相比《壮游》，他更喜欢《Top Gear》。《Top Gear》“变得越来越好”，但《壮游》“显得更流程化、不自然、像被强迫……注意力常常从汽车上被拉走，因为名为克拉克森的主持人似乎只想要话题和头条“。安德森还表示，演播帐篷桥段很快就变得重复，尤其是“明星脑碰脑”环节，而且三位主持人似乎花费太多的时间彼此针锋相对，测试车手麦克·斯金纳也没有提供有意义的评论。<ref name="anderson-20170417">{{cite web|first=Brad|last=Anderson|date=2017-04-17|work=Car Scoops|title=Sorry The Grand Tour, Top Gear Is Again The World's Best Car Show|url=http://www.carscoops.com/2017/04/sorry-grand-tour-top-gear-is-again.html|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430103555/http://www.carscoops.com/2017/04/sorry-grand-tour-top-gear-is-again.html|archivedate=2017-04-30}}</ref>

根据[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上收集的8篇评价文章，有7篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”达88%，平均得分8.0（最高10分）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/the_grand_tour/s01|title=The Grand Tour: Season 1 – Rotten Tomatoes|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2017-07-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127205709/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/the_grand_tour/s01|archivedate=2017-11-27}}</ref>

《[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]》给予第二季第一集积极的评价，称“此集低调的首映表明节目找到了它的节奏”。<ref>{{cite news|title=The Grand Tour season 2 episode 1 review: We're in safe hands as Clarkson, Hammond and May return|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-grand-tour/feature/a844965/the-grand-tour-season-2-episode-1-review/|publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|accessdate=2017-12-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171209043915/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/the-grand-tour/feature/a844965/the-grand-tour-season-2-episode-1-review/|archivedate=2017-12-09}}</ref>《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》同样给出正面评价，给予节目4星评分（最高5星），并表示“节目某些部分比较平淡，但大多数行之有效，节目制作水准高，且肯定投入了一卡车的钱”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/television-review-the-grand-tour-on-amazon-prime-dc7gtbrfq|title=Television review: The Grand Tour on Amazon Prime|website=[[The_Times|The Times]]|accessdate=2017-12-08|archive-date=2019-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916012202/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/television-review-the-grand-tour-on-amazon-prime-dc7gtbrfq}}</ref>尽管《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》没有作出积极评价，但依然对此集表示赞许，称“剧情依然差劲。克拉克森给梅的新绰号‘果莓手泵’甚至没能逗笑那些在伦敦观看首映的超级粉丝”，但也表示“每次节目摇摆不定时，《壮游》总能复现《Top Gear》最擅长的聪明技巧——逗笑观众的同时插入一些严肃的汽车测评”。最终此集获得3星评分（最高5星）。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/grand-tour-season-2-episode-1-review-has-jeremy-clarkson-finally/|title=The Grand Tour season 2, episode 1 review: Has Jeremy Clarkson finally found his groove?|last=|first=|date=|work=|accessdate=2017-12-08|publisher=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171208005200/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/on-demand/0/grand-tour-season-2-episode-1-review-has-jeremy-clarkson-finally/|archivedate=2017-12-08}}</ref>

《[[广播时报|广播时报]]》批评“明星面面碰”嘉宾性别不平衡。只有剧集《Oh, Canada》中出现唯一一名女性嘉宾[[帕丽斯·希尔顿|帕丽斯·希尔顿]]。<ref name="RadioTimes 271117">{{cite web|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/tv/2017-11-27/the-grand-tour-celebrity-guests-season-2/|title=The Grand Tour's first celebrity guests for series 2 have been revealed – and there's not a single woman|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2017-12-20|first=Thomas|last=Ling|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222051333/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/tv/2017-11-27/the-grand-tour-celebrity-guests-season-2/|archivedate=2017-12-22}}</ref>

