== 电子游戏 ==
2019年1月15日，{{le|亚马逊游戏工作室|Amazon Game Studios}}和第三季节目同步在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台上线游戏《{{le|The Grand Tour Game|The Grand Tour Game}}》<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.engadget.com/2018/08/21/amazon-turned-the-grand-tour-tv-series-into-racing-game/ | title = Amazon turned its ‘The Grand Tour’ TV series into a racing game | first = David | last = Lumb | date = 2018-08-21 | accessdate = 2019-01-30 | work = Engadget | archive-date = 2019-05-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190503223637/https://www.engadget.com/2018/08/21/amazon-turned-the-grand-tour-tv-series-into-racing-game/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.engadget.com/2018/08/23/grand-tour-video-game-demo-gamescom/ | title = ‘The Grand Tour Game’ is a near-perfect mirror of the show | first = Nick | last = Summers | date = 2019-08-23 | work = [[Engadget|Engadget]] | access-date = 2019-03-29 | archive-date = 2019-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327183812/https://www.engadget.com/2018/08/23/grand-tour-video-game-demo-gamescom/ }}</ref>。在这款章回体休闲[[竞速游戏|竞速游戏]]中，玩家可以驾驶节目中的车辆参与挑战。游戏内容与节目同步更新，玩家可以参与其中的15项全新挑战。除了单人游戏模式，玩家还可以在部分挑战中采用分屏多人模式。各章节内容包含节目画面，主持人克拉克森、梅、哈蒙德为游戏配音<ref>{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2019/gaming/news/the-grand-tour-game-amazon-game-studios-1203101360/ | title = ‘The Grand Tour Game’ Puts Emphasis On Fun, ‘Playing the Show’ | first = Brittany | last = Vincent | date = 2019-01-07 | accessdate = 2019-01-30 | work = Variety | archive-date = 2019-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190927171839/https://variety.com/2019/gaming/news/the-grand-tour-game-amazon-game-studios-1203101360/ }}</ref>。

游戏上线以来，评论家们对此褒贬不一。游戏对节目拍摄场景和车辆的还原度较大，吸引节目和杰瑞米·克拉克森的粉丝们游玩是一大亮点。不过，驾驶控制和部分挑战重复多次的设计遭到批评。尽管如此，节目的粉丝们还是给游戏打出了积极的评价<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-01-17-the-grand-tour-game-is-a-bad-game-but-an-interesting-vision-for-interactive-tv|title=The Grand Tour Game is a bad game, but an interesting vision for interactive TV|website=www.eurogamer.net|author=Oli Welsh|accessdate=2019-01-17|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111230842/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-01-17-the-grand-tour-game-is-a-bad-game-but-an-interesting-vision-for-interactive-tv}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.driving.co.uk/news/products/grand-tour-game-review/|title=THE GRAND TOUR GAME REVIEW - Our thoughts on The Grand Tour Game so far|website=driving.co.uk|publisher=Sunday Times|author=Will Dron|accessdate=2019-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118233616/https://www.driving.co.uk/news/products/grand-tour-game-review/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://metro.co.uk/2019/01/21/the-grand-tour-game-review-interactive-tv-8367126/|title=The Grand Tour Game review – interactive TV|website=metro.co.uk|author=Jim Hargreaves|accessdate=2019-01-21|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102150105/https://metro.co.uk/2019/01/21/the-grand-tour-game-review-interactive-tv-8367126/}}</ref>。

